name: WoW Draenai
description:
Trained 40+ images (fan art, renders, cosplay) for over 20k steps on SD1.5, and it's still finicky, especially for photo-realistic models. (It's like they haven't seen a woman with purple skin and horns before.) It really likes Anything-V3.

"Female draenai" should get you the best results. (Not enough source material for males.)

Now... Show Me What You Got!
